@startuml
title SmartQueue - Customer Service Flow (Activity)

start

:Customer opens app;

if (Has appointment?) then (Yes)
  :Check appointment status;
  :Check in;
else (No)
  :Join virtual queue;
endif

:Wait for turn;

:Staff calls next customer;

if (Customer responds?) then (Yes)
  :Provide service;
  :Complete service;
else (No)
  :Mark no-show;
endif

stop
@enduml
